---

## Code Snippets and Context

### PowerShell Script for Project Organization

```powershell
# C:\TheTradingRobotPlugWeb\Powershells\maintenance\tree.ps1

Get-ChildItem -Path "C:\TheTradingRobotPlugWeb" -Recurse | 
    Sort-Object -Property FullName | 
    Format-List -Property FullName
```

This script outputs the entire directory structure of the project, helping verify that everything is organized as intended.

